>
> Curious what the most read magazines in your house are?

> Wonder what one I should try next?

Our family subscribes to the following magazines:

Spider
Click
NG Kids
Lego
Cooks Illustrated
Fine Woodworking
Harper's
Mother Jones
Paddlesports Business
Utne Reader
Sea Kayaker
Mother Earth News
Woman's Day
Cooking Light
People
HEM
Life Learning

We used to subscribe to Ladybug and All Round too.

I too LOVE magazines and I'm always checking our more from the library.
Mothering, National Geographic, and Good Housekeeping are favorites.

Jen
